son\", \"from\": 5262, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"n'est pas autoris\\u00e9\", \"from\": 5279, \"to\": 5297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"M\\u00eame dans les pays en voie de d\\u00e9veloppement, ces op\\u00e9rations sont co\\u00fbteuses.\", \"from\": 5301, \"to\": 5377, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5307, \"end\": 5311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"en voie de d\\u00e9veloppement\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5345}, {\"ngram\": \"ces op\\u00e9rations sont co\\u00fbteuses\", \"from\": 5347, \"to\": 5376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Si Imane avait les moyens de faire ce dont les gens l'accusent, elle pr\\u00e9f\\u00e9rerait se nourrir, acheter du pain et des v\\u00eatements et vivre comme le reste de ses amis\\\", affirme-t-il.\", \"from\": 5378, \"to\": 5555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Si Imane avait\", \"from\": 5378, \"to\": 5392}, {\"ngram\": \"les moyens de faire ce\", \"from\": 5393, \"to\": 5415}, {\"ngram\": \"gens l'accusent\", \"from\": 5425, \"to\": 5440}, {\"ngram\": \"elle pr\\u00e9f\\u00e9rerait se nourrir\", \"from\": 5442, \"to\": 5469}, {\"ngram\": \"et vivre comme le reste de ses amis\", \"from\": 5504, \"to\": 5539}, {\"ngram\": \"affirme-t-il\", \"from\": 5542, \"to\": 5554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif \\u00e9tait en larmes apr\\u00e8s sa victoire contre la Hongroise Anna Hamori qui l'a qualifi\\u00e9e pour les demi-finales.\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5557, \"end\": 5569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"apr\\u00e8s sa victoire contre\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5610}, {\"ngram\": \"la Hongroise Anna Hamori qui\", \"from\": 5611, \"to\": 5639}, {\"ngram\": \"l'a qualifi\\u00e9e pour les demi\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5667}, {\"ngram\": \"finales\", \"from\": 5668, \"to\": 5675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dans l'interview, la boxeuse affirme que\\\"les obstacles motivent la volont\\u00e9\\\", une affirmation \\u00e0 laquelle elle dit croire depuis son plus jeune \\u00e2ge.\", \"from\": 5678, \"to\": 5824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"la boxeuse\", \"from\": 5696, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"que\\\"les obstacles motivent la volont\\u00e9\", \"from\": 5715, \"to\": 5752}, {\"ngram\": \"depuis\", \"from\": 5798, \"to\": 5804}, {\"ngram\": \"son\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5808}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2ge\", \"from\": 5820, \"to\": 5823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"La jeune femme de 25 ans a clairement indiqu\\u00e9 qu'elle ferait tout pour remporter la premi\\u00e8re m\\u00e9daille d'or olympique de l'Alg\\u00e9rie en boxe f\\u00e9minine, malgr\\u00e9 les accusations dont elle est la cible.\", \"from\": 5826, \"to\": 6020, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"La\", \"from\": 5826, \"to\": 5828}, {\"ngram\": \"de 25 ans\", \"from\": 5841, \"to\": 5850}, {\"ngram\": \"a clairement indiqu\\u00e9\", \"from\": 5851, \"to\": 5871}, {\"ngram\": \"pour remporter\", \"from\": 5892, \"to\": 5906}, {\"ngram\": \"premi\\u00e8re\", \"from\": 5910, \"to\": 5918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imane Khelif a \\u00e9galement remerci\\u00e9 le Comit\\u00e9 international olympique pour son soutien pendant la pol\\u00e9mique qui a suivi son admission aux JO de Paris.\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6022, \"end\": 6034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\u00e9galement remerci\\u00e9 le Comit\\u00e9 international olympique pour son\", \"from\": 6035, \"to\": 6098}, {\"ngram\": \"soutien pendant\", \"from\": 6099, \"to\": 6114}, {\"ngram\": \"pol\\u00e9mique qui\", \"from\": 6118, \"to\": 6131}, {\"ngram\": \"a suivi son admission\", \"from\": 6132, \"to\": 6153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Elle a ajout\\u00e9 que le pr\\u00e9sident du CIO, Thomas Bach, lui avait envoy\\u00e9 un message personnel dans lequel il la soutenait et l'encourageait.\", \"from\": 6171, \"to\": 6307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6171, \"end\": 6175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elle_Bishop\", \"score\": 0.5727041298631317, \"rank\": 0.7451103653335893, \"text\": \"Elle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elle_Bishop\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elle_Bishop\"}, {\"begin\": 6205, \"end\": 6208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"score\": 0.7868654575424009, \"rank\": 0.2708561085969607, \"text\": \"CIO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q178790\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Congress_of_Industrial_Organizations\"}, {\"begin\": 6210, \"end\": 6221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}, {\"begin\": 6261, \"end\": 6265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lequel il la soutenait et l'encourageait\", \"from\": 6266, \"to\": 6306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Je tiens \\u00e0 remercier tous ceux qui m'ont soutenue, tous les Alg\\u00e9riens et Alg\\u00e9riennes, tous les peuples du monde arabe et du monde entier qui se sont tenus \\u00e0 mes c\\u00f4t\\u00e9s dans cette campagne acharn\\u00e9e contre moi\\\", d\\u00e9clare-t-elle.\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6534, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6477, \"end\": 6481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"dans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Agency_for_National_Security\"}, {\"begin\": 6482, \"end\": 6487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\", \"score\": 0.997609014051072, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"cette\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e8te\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Je tiens\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6318}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e0 remercier tous ceux qui m'ont soutenue\", \"from\": 6319, \"to\": 6359}, {\"ngram\": \"tous les Alg\\u00e9riens et Alg\\u00e9riennes\", \"from\": 6361, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"tous les peuples\", \"from\": 6396, \"to\": 6412}, {\"ngram\": \"arabe\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6427}, {\"ngram\": \"d\\u00e9clare-t-elle\", \"from\": 6519, \"to\": 6533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angela Carini a depuis exprim\\u00e9 sa tristesse face \\u00e0 cette controverse et s'est excus\\u00e9e aupr\\u00e8s d'Imane Khelif.\", \"from\": 6536, \"to\": 6644, \"en